In[15]:
files = []
files.append('images/AlaskanMalamute.jpg')
files.append('images/AmericanEskimo.jpg')
files.append('images/AmericanFoxhound.jpg')
files.append('images/AustralianTerrier.jpg')
files.append('images/Basenji.jpg')
files.append('images/Beagle.jpg')
In[17]:
imgs = []
for f in files:
    imgs.append(cv2.imread(f))
In[18]:
plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10), dpi=80)
nrows = 2
ncols = 3
for i in range(nrows*ncols):
    plt.subplot(nrows, ncols, i+1)
    plt.imshow(imgs[i])

OpenCV BGR (Blue Green Red) RGB (Red Green Blue) OpenCV cvtColor

In[19]:
plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10), dpi=80)
nrows = 2
ncols = 3
for i in range(nrows*ncols):
    plt.subplot(nrows, ncols, i+1)
    plt.imshow(cv2.cvtColor(imgs[i], cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB))
